rm <b>16</b> via a tolerance ring <b>12,</b> the pivot bearing being configured to swing around the shaft. The number of balls of each ball bearing <b>20</b> and the number of concave portions of the tolerance ring <b>12,</b> which are configured to press the outer ring <b>25,</b> are relatively prime to each other. Accordingly, it is possible to inexpensively make the reliable pivot bearing that achieves high precision with a simple structure, and thus a reliable high density magnetic recording apparatus is provided.</p></abstract></us-patent-application>